casebody.data:
LIME LOUNGE, LLC, and Thunder & Lightning, Inc., Plaintiffs-Appellants,
v.
ZONING BOARD OF ADJUSTMENT OF the CITY OF DES MOINES, Iowa, Defendant-Appellee. No. 18-0155 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed February 6, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Lime Lounge, LLC, and Thunder & Lightning, Inc., appeal the revocation of the conditional use permit issued by the zoning board. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
